S.FORM: Jianshi Jianshi gu icuwa i Hsinchu. ala atjunangn mapuljat 522.98 km² (ma'linpan atjunang 397.38 km², ma'linaule atjunang 114.53 km²). ala caucau mapuljat 9,456 caucau, ala daceneqlan mapuljat 2,825 a daceneqlan, Tayal (91%) a maqcuwa caucau. imaza a kinapungadan aicu a nahuy na siayaya a kakaian na tayal. a i tjaikacedas a navalj a nahuy i tua hsinchu king na taiwan. sipaljavaljavak na sihu tucu ta nahuy a jianshi gu. pulingetjan a kadjunangan naicu a pinaljavakan a 527.5795 km² imaza. pinaljavakan aicu a jianshi gu a tjaljaqaca i tua hsinchu king. kinamamamawan tua vavavan nua gadugadu imaza a kemasi ta 200m a patje 2000m. kinaizuan aicu a qinaljan na caucau se tayal imaza. na semanumaq a ngaingai kata zuma a zuku se ciuku tjaivililj. papungadan a sihu tucu tamaza ta jianshi. a kakaian na ciuku a siayaya a jianshi taza tjagulj a ita imaza ayatua nginiraqan a kadjunangan na veljeluan na yulje. kadjunangan tjaikacedas aicu a nahuy ta minnao na yilan king; tjaikacedas a viri ta fuxing gu na taoyuan; tjaiviri ta guanxi gu; tjainavalj ta taian na miaoli king; tjaikaledep ta tatoba' kata hengshan gu. cinalivatan na sipaljavak nia dripung taza lizuk a sihu na hsinchu ciu kacavilj a 1920. tjaiteku a pinaljavakan ta hsinchu ciu aicu a zhudong kun. imaza a pasakacedas a viri ta zhudong kun aicu a pinaljavakan na pukinsacan a zhudong. ljakua izua za 玉峰村 na jianshi gu tucu a tazua pinaljavakan na taki kun . kikarivuanan i tapong i tapong a gaduan izua tjelu a kikarivuanan na tayal ta dripung a kemasi ta kacavilj a 1910 a patje kacavilj a 1913. kiqecevan na tayal i syakaro malailaing ti sakuma samata se dripung a kata sivitay nimadju a mangetjez a semamaza kacavilj a 1913. kiqecev a tayal ta sivitay se dripung a kemasi tazua kacavilj a 1913 a patje kacavilj a 1926. mavan pinavavecikan nia tayal kata dripung aicu a 埋石之盟 a semkez taza kikarivuanan tjaivililj. paljavak tua atjunang matja 7 qinaljan i Jianshi. matja 49 qinaljan imaza, Mkzihing , Mkmatuy , Ｐiling , Paqiy , Yutak , Kbaqeh , Cinbulan , Kuxan , Ageq , Micista , Mknahuy , Mksuzing , Mklapay , Lkuxan , Hbun-Rangay , Mkslaq , Qalang-Qwayux , Hbun-Qramay , Pololan , Uraw , Libu , Llyung , Ulay , Batul , Ｍami , Ｑuri , Ｐlmwan , Tayax , Ponaway , Smangus , Thyakan , Smangus , Cinsbu , Yuluw , Gowryu , Rahaw , Cyocuy , Hbun kramay , Hbun-tunan , Kin lwan , Qolu , Qyuws , Hbun-lesa , Metapay , M'yutak , Mrmurak , Spwan , Melukux , Metuiy . pinaljavakan kinatuluan izua tapuluq saka ita a gakku a kedrikedri. sipacacikelan palidring a djalan sikamasan 120 a palidring a djalan na hsinchu king, a kemasi ta 橫山鄉 a patjemaza i nahuy(jianshi gu) basu na hsinchu sikamasan 5625 sikamasan 5631 kivangavangan

Jianshi Jianshi go icowa i Hsincho. ala atjonangn mapoljat 522.98 km² (ma'linpan atjonang 397.38 km², ma'linaole atjonang 114.53 km²). ala caocao mapoljat 9,456 caocao, ala daceneqlan mapoljat 2,825 a daceneqlan, Tayal (91%) a maqcowa caocao. imaza a kinapongadan aico a nahoy na siayaya a kakaian na tayal. a i tjaikacedas a navalj a nahoy i toa hsincho king na taiwan. sipaljavaljavak na siho toco ta nahoy a jianshi go. polingetjan a kadjonangan naico a pinaljavakan a 527.5795 km² imaza. pinaljavakan aico a jianshi go a tjaljaqaca i toa hsincho king. kinamamamawan toa vavavan noa gadogado imaza a kemasi ta 200m a patje 2000m. kinaizoan aico a qinaljan na caocao se tayal imaza. na semanomaq a ngaingai kata zoma a zoko se cioko tjaivililj. papongadan a siho toco tamaza ta jianshi. a kakaian na cioko a siayaya a jianshi taza tjagolj a ita imaza ayatoa nginiraqan a kadjonangan na veljeloan na yolje. kadjonangan tjaikacedas aico a nahoy ta minnao na yilan king; tjaikacedas a viri ta foxing go na taoyoan; tjaiviri ta goanxi go; tjainavalj ta taian na miaoli king; tjaikaledep ta tatoba' kata hengshan go. cinalivatan na sipaljavak nia dripong taza lizok a siho na hsincho cio kacavilj a 1920. tjaiteko a pinaljavakan ta hsincho cio aico a zhodong kon. imaza a pasakacedas a viri ta zhodong kon aico a pinaljavakan na pokinsacan a zhodong. ljakoa izoa za 玉峰村 na jianshi go toco a tazoa pinaljavakan na taki kon . kikarivoanan i tapong i tapong a gadoan izoa tjelo a kikarivoanan na tayal ta dripong a kemasi ta kacavilj a 1910 a patje kacavilj a 1913. kiqecevan na tayal i syakaro malailaing ti sakoma samata se dripong a kata sivitay nimadjo a mangetjez a semamaza kacavilj a 1913. kiqecev a tayal ta sivitay se dripong a kemasi tazoa kacavilj a 1913 a patje kacavilj a 1926. mavan pinavavecikan nia tayal kata dripong aico a 埋石之盟 a semkez taza kikarivoanan tjaivililj. paljavak toa atjonang matja 7 qinaljan i Jianshi. matja 49 qinaljan imaza, Mkzihing , Mkmatoy , Ｐiling , Paqiy , Yotak , Kbaqeh , Cinbolan , Koxan , Ageq , Micista , Mknahoy , Mksozing , Mklapay , Lkoxan , Hbon-Rangay , Mkslaq , Qalang-Qwayox , Hbon-Qramay , Pololan , Uraw , Libo , Llyong , Ulay , Batol , Ｍami , Ｑori , Ｐlmwan , Tayax , Ponaway , Smangos , Thyakan , Smangos , Cinsbo , Yolow , Gowryo , Rahaw , Cyocoy , Hbon kramay , Hbon-tonan , Kin lwan , Qolo , Qyows , Hbon-lesa , Metapay , M'yotak , Mrmorak , Spwan , Melokox , Metoiy . pinaljavakan kinatoloan izoa tapoloq saka ita a gakko a kedrikedri. sipacacikelan palidring a djalan sikamasan 120 a palidring a djalan na hsincho king, a kemasi ta 橫山鄉 a patjemaza i nahoy(jianshi go) baso na hsincho sikamasan 5625 sikamasan 5631 kivangavangan
